creator: So Dialed
descriptionHtml:
Need to keep score at your rock crawling events? Get So Dialed's Crawl Scorekeeper to help you calculate the points for both crawls and scale points. Keep a log of the runs you've scored, so you can easily record them at the end of the round or event.

Features:

CRAWL POINTS
- Record crawl points for progress, gates, reverses, winches, rollovers, touches, and bonuses
- Use SORRCA points for each category, or set your own for club crawls
- Set custom time limits and point-outs
- Log DNFs
- Save all runs to a log, so the event organizer can easily record them - no screenshots necessary (1 week history)

SCALE POINTS
- Record scale points by official SORRCA rules
- Quick and easy form with scoring criteria, checkboxes, and buttons (no typing!)
- Log scale scores for reporting to the event organizer
descriptionShort: The only rock crawl scorekeeper you will ever need.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Improved performance of drop-downs.
